      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 Solution"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The build and release management of multiple applications, web portals and middle wares wasn’t an easy task. The customer is also required to have a disaster recovery mechanism in place so that in case the primary region goes down everything can be replicated into another region to keep their operations running."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "To resolve the issue regarding the production environment, we suggested following these steps for segregation."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Continuous Integration of all the mobile"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Continuous Delivery for the same is achieved"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Mobile application builds distribution is achieved"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The whole Infrastructure deployment is done"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure DevOps automation was employed for"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure AD Application registrations were also"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The automation is being performed for all the"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "A secondary Azure region is also set up for"
        }
      ],
